<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reschedule Request Rejected</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .logo {
            max-width: 150px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #dc2626;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .doctor-info {
            background-color: #f0f9ff;
            border: 1px solid #bae6fd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .doctor-info h3 {
            color: #1e3a8a;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .doctor-info h3::before {
            content: "üë®‚Äç‚öïÔ∏è";
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .doctor-name {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e3a8a;
        }
        
        .schedule-comparison {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .schedule-box {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .schedule-box.maintained {
            border-left: 4px solid #059669;
        }
        
        .schedule-box.rejected {
            border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
        }
        
        .schedule-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .schedule-title.maintained::before {
            content: "‚úÖ";
            margin-right: 8px;
        }
        
        .schedule-title.rejected::before {
            content: "‚ùå";
            margin-right: 8px;
        }
        
        .schedule-title.maintained {
            color: #059669;
        }
        
        .schedule-title.rejected {
            color: #dc2626;
        }
        
        .schedule-detail {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .schedule-detail:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .schedule-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .schedule-value {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .rejection-reason {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .rejection-reason strong {
            color: #dc2626;
        }
        
        .maintained-appointment {
            background-color: #f0fdf4;
            border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .details-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #059669;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .details-title::before {
            content: "üìã";
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 12px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
        }
        
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
            min-width: 120px;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            color: #6b7280;
            text-align: right;
            flex: 1;
        }
        
        .next-steps {
            background-color: #eff6ff;
            border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .next-steps h3 {
            color: #1e3a8a;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .next-steps ul {
            margin-left: 20px;
            color: #374151;
        }
        
        .next-steps li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .appointment-id {
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 12px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .appointment-id strong {
            color: #1e3a8a;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #3b82f6 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(30, 58, 138, 0.3);
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 25px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .contact-info {
            color: #1e3a8a;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .content {
                padding: 25px 20px;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
            
            .schedule-comparison {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 15px;
            }
            
            .detail-row {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                text-align: left;
            }
            
            .detail-value {
                text-align: left;
                margin-top: 5px;
            }
            
            .schedule-detail {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                text-align: left;
            }
            
            .schedule-value {
                margin-top: 5px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://sidclinic.com/logo.jpeg" alt="SID Clinic Logo" class="logo">
            <h1>Reschedule Request Rejected</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="status-badge">‚ùå Request Rejected</div>
            
            <div class="greeting">Dear {{patientName}},</div>
            
            <div class="message">
                We regret to inform you that your reschedule request has been rejected by your doctor. 
                Your original appointment time has been maintained. We understand this may be disappointing, 
                and we want to assure you that this decision was made after careful consideration.
            </div>
            
            <div class="doctor-info">
                <h3>Doctor Information</h3>
                <div class="doctor-name">Dr. {{doctorName}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="schedule-comparison">
                <div class="schedule-box maintained">
                    <div class="schedule-title maintained">Maintained Schedule</div>
                    
                    <div class="schedule-detail">
                        <span class="schedule-label">Date:</span>
                        <span class="schedule-value">{{originalDate}}</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="schedule-detail">
                        <span class="schedule-label">Time:</span>
                        <span class="schedule-value">{{originalTime}}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="schedule-box rejected">
                    <div class="schedule-title rejected">Rejected Request</div>
                    
                    <div class="schedule-detail">
                        <span class="schedule-label">Date:</span>
                        <span class="schedule-value">{{newDate}}</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="schedule-detail">
                        <span class="schedule-label">Time:</span>
                        <span class="schedule-value">{{newTime}}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            {{#if rejectionReason}}
            <div class="rejection-reason">
                <strong>Reason for Rejection:</strong><br>
                {{rejectionReason}}
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div class="maintained-appointment">
                <div class="details-title">Your Confirmed Appointment</div>
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Doctor:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">Dr. {{doctorName}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Date:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{originalDate}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Time:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{originalTime}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Appointment ID:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">#{{appointmentId}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="next-steps">
                <h3>What You Can Do Next:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Attend your original appointment as scheduled</li>
                    <li>Contact our support team if you have urgent concerns</li>
                    <li>Consider booking a new appointment for a different time</li>
                    <li>Discuss alternative arrangements directly with your doctor</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="appointment-id">
                <strong>Appointment ID:</strong> #{{appointmentId}}
            </div>
            
            <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="cta-button">View Appointment Details</a>
            
            <div class="message">
                We apologize for any inconvenience this may have caused. Your original appointment 
                time is still confirmed and we look forward to seeing you as scheduled.
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for choosing SID Clinic for your healthcare needs.</p>
            <p class="contact-info">Need help? Contact us at support@sidclinic.com</p>
            <p>¬© 2024 SID Clinic. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>


